  [ 15] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [ 17] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <1>
  [ 19] extcall 9 ............................... return 1
  [ 21] ret
end

on updateStuffdata me, tValue
  [  0] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [  2] getparam 1 .............................. <tValue>
  [  4] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, tValue>
  [  6] objcall 220 ............................. me.setState(tValue)
