end

on update me
  [  0] getprop 287 ............................. <pState>
  [  3] pushcons 0 .............................. <"1">
  [  5] nteq .................................... <pState <> "1">
  [  6] jmpifz [ 15] ............................ if pState <> "1" then
  [  9] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [ 11] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <1>
  [ 13] extcall 9 ............................... return 1
  [ 15] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
